data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stately 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem is a true masterpiece, perfectly nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac within the serene county, where you can enjoy the perks of no city taxes or HOA fees. With over 2,200 square feet of beautifully updated living space, this residence offers a harmonious blend of comfort and style. As you enter the welcoming front entrance, you'll immediately appreciate the charming curb appeal and the well-maintained landscaping. The split floor plan ensures privacy and convenience, making this home an ideal choice for all. The heart of this home is the spacious and bright living room, featuring an inviting fireplace that's perfect for cozy fall evenings. The adjoining dining area offers plenty of room for gatherings with friends and family. A chef's dream kitchen awaits you, complete with modern appliances, ample cabinetry, and an island, making meal preparation a breeze. The primary suite is a retreat of its own, boasting a generous bedroom, a walk-in closet, and a luxurious ensuite bathroom with a dual vanity, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. The two additional bedrooms are equally inviting, and the second full bathroom is tastefully updated, ensuring the utmost in comfort for all. This home's location is a real standout - just minutes away from the Piney Green Gate, Main Gate, and Wilson Gate of Camp Lejeune, making it an excellent choice for military moving to the area. You'll also appreciate the convenience of being close to all town amenities, including shopping, dining, and entertainment. Exit outside to the back patio, where you can enjoy your morning coffee or host barbecues in the spacious, fenced backyard. The peaceful cul-de-sac location ensures minimal through traffic, providing a serene environment to thrive in. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a meticulously maintained and beautifully updated home in a prime location. Schedule your showing today and experience the best of Onslow Count
